{
  "id": "adv_main_01_02_04",
  "title": "星見編1章10話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうして物置で寝泊まりしなきゃ\nならないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do I have to sleep\nin the shed?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9798808657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "いいじゃん\n{user}くんらしくって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why not?\nIt’s your style‚ {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 7.059433150291447
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "俺らしいってどういうことだよ！\n麻奈の時はこんなことなかったのにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How exactly is this my style?!\nHow come I never went through this abuse with you‚ Mana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.614144925637682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 12.828526186943023
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ三枝さんがいたし\n変なことしてもぶっ飛ばせる自信もあったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ because Saegusa-san was there for one.\nAnd I was always ready to punch you out if there were anything naughty.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あのな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.42852618694306,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 20.9
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 21.19519285360973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（ここ星見市は、都心から電車で一時間ほどの所にある）\n（どこにでもあるような町だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is Hoshimi City‚ a typical town）\n（about an hour away from Tokyo by train.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.928526186943063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（流星群が綺麗に見える町というこの名前にちなんで）\n（夏には流星群を見る祭も開かれている）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s named “Hoshimi” after the meteor showers you can see clearly here‚）\n（and it hosts summer festivals to celebrate these stars.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.933333333333337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（――長瀬麻奈。この町から突如現れたアイドルが）\n（育った町として星見市は有名になった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana Nagase appeared out of nowhere and make Hoshimi well-known.）\n（Hoshimi came to be known as the town that birthed the “Miracle of the Star”.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（そして彼女がホストを務めた流星群のお祭は）\n（過去最大の来場者を集め、町は人で埋め尽くされた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（And the meteor shower festival that she hosted）\n（had the highest attendance in history. The streets were packed.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "何考えてたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’re you thinking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "お祭の時、覚えてる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ do you remember that festival?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "忘れられないな\n大変だったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How could I forget it?\nIt was a nightmare.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "私は楽しかったよ\nすごく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it was fun!\nA lot….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 67.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 67.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 67.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "海に行こう、私も見たい\n流星群",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s go to the beach.\nI wanna see the meteor shower.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 72.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "無茶言うなよ\n今、どれだけ人がいると思ってるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be silly.\nDo you realize how crowded it is right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 77.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "私がホストなんだよ\nなのに、私が見られないなんておかしくない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’m the host.\nAnd I don’t even get to see the meteor shower? How fair is that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 82.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "もう後はみんなで流星群見て終わりでしょ\nだったらいいよ、行こうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And my hosting duties are basically over now anyway.\nCome on! Let’s go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "近くにいる人にバレたらどうする\n今の長瀬麻奈は、超人気アイドルなんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if people recognize you?\nDon’t forget‚ Mana‚ you’re a superstar now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage3",
      "startTime": 95.43333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "変装すれば大丈夫だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll just wear a disguise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 99.16666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 102.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "わあ……綺麗……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… It’s beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "大きな声出すとバレる\nサングラスずらさないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t shout. You’ll blow your cover.\nAnd keep your sunglasses on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "だって見えないんだもん\n大丈夫、平気平気",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can’t see.\nDon’t worry‚ we’re fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……私、小さい頃からこの町住んでるけど\nこんなに星見るの初めてかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… I’ve lived in this town all my life‚\nbut this might be my best view of the stars ever…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about you‚ {user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.26666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "…………どうかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……{user}くんらしい\nつまんない答え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… That's so {user}.\nWhat a boring answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.26666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_04-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "面白くなくて、すみませんね\nここ、人多いから、もう少しこっちに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ excuse me for being boring.\nIt’s too crowded over here. Let’s move.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
